  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">"🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — ADR-015 binding event-shape definition; user-content leakage prevention by typing construction."</step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">Read TASK-INDEX; confirm 053 complete.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">Read existing PaneEventTypes.ts to map current shape + extension pattern.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Define New Types">Add 6 discriminated-union variants to `context` channel. Each payload typed with explicit + enumerated fields ONLY; no `unknown`/`any` content fields.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Export + Document">JSDoc each variant citing ADR-015 + FR-37. Export from `@spaarke/ai-widgets` barrel.</step>
