    <step order="6" name="ADR-015 Audit">Code review every payload field — confirm no `content: string`, no `userMessage: string`, no free-form text fields that could leak user input. Document audit in task notes.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-012/015/030).</step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">TASK-INDEX 059 ✅.</step>
